---------------------------------------------------------
RNA-Seq Pipeline .gitignore
---------------------------------------------------------

1. Raw Data and Output Directories

Ignore the specific directories where we store data and outputs

c_sparklecode/
d_data/
o_outputs/
n_notes/

2. Sequence Files

Ignore all raw and intermediate sequence files

*.fastq
*.fq
*.fastq.gz
*.fq.gz
*.gz

3. Alignment Files

BAM files are massive binary files and should never be committed

*.bam
*.bai
*.bam.bai
*.sam

4. STAR Alignment Intermediates & Logs

Ignore STAR's highly verbose output logs and temporary folders

*Log.final.out
*Log.out
*Log.progress.out
*SJ.out.tab
*_STARgenome/
*_STARpass1/
*_STARtmp/

5. Quality Control Reports & Logs

Ignore HTML/JSON reports from fastp and run logs from umi_tools

*.html
*.json
*.log
dedup_stats

6. Count Matrices

Depending on the number of samples, these can get large

gene_counts.txt
gene_counts.txt.summary

7. OS Generated Files (Mac/Linux)

.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db